ivardefs.name: exclude
ivardefs.desc: When true, members with this characteristic are excluded from the element.

ivardefs.name: participantEffectiveDescription
ivardefs.desc: A narrative description of the time period the study covers.

ivardefs.name: participantEffectiveGroupMeasure
ivardefs.desc: Indicates how elements are aggregated within the study effective period.

ivardefs.name: participantEffectiveTimeFromStart
ivardefs.desc: Indicates duration from the participant's study entry.

ivardefs.name: studyEffectiveDescription
ivardefs.desc: A narrative description of the time period the study covers.

ivardefs.name: studyEffectiveGroupMeasure
ivardefs.desc: Indicates how elements are aggregated within the study effective period.

ivardefs.name: studyEffectiveTimeFromStart
ivardefs.desc: Indicates duration from the study initiation.

ivardefs.name: unitOfMeasure
ivardefs.desc: Specifies the UCUM unit for the outcome.

ivardefs.name: usageContext_
ivardefs.desc: Use UsageContext to define the members of the population, such as Age Ranges, Genders, Settings.

properties.desc: A characteristic that defines the members of the research element. Multiple characteristics are applied with "and" semantics.
